{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Amatsia, roi de Juda. Victoire sur les \u00c9domites<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. 2 R 14:1-7. 2 Co 6:14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Amatsia devint roi \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e2ge de vingt-cinq ans, et il r\u00e9gna vingt-neuf ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Joaddan, de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.2","name":"2 Chroniques 25:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.27","name":"2 Chroniques 24:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mais avec un c\u0153ur qui n\u2019\u00e9tait pas enti\u00e8rement d\u00e9vou\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.3","name":"2 Chroniques 25:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.1","name":"2 Chroniques 25:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Lorsque la royaut\u00e9 fut affermie entre ses mains, il fit p\u00e9rir ses serviteurs qui avaient tu\u00e9 le roi son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.4","name":"2 Chroniques 25:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.2","name":"2 Chroniques 25:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Mais il ne fit pas mourir leurs fils, car il agit selon ce qui est \u00e9crit dans la loi, dans le livre de Mo\u00efse, o\u00f9 l\u2019\u00c9ternel donne ce commandement: On ne fera point mourir les p\u00e8res pour les enfants, et l\u2019on ne fera point mourir les enfants pour les p\u00e8res; mais on fera mourir chacun pour son p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.5","name":"2 Chroniques 25:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.3","name":"2 Chroniques 25:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Amatsia rassembla les hommes de Juda et les pla\u00e7a d\u2019apr\u00e8s les maisons paternelles, les chefs de milliers et les chefs de centaines, pour tout Juda et Benjamin; il en fit le d\u00e9nombrement depuis l\u2019\u00e2ge de vingt ans et au-dessus, et il trouva trois cent mille hommes d\u2019\u00e9lite, en \u00e9tat de porter les armes, maniant la lance et le bouclier.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.6","name":"2 Chroniques 25:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.4","name":"2 Chroniques 25:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il prit encore \u00e0 sa solde dans Isra\u00ebl cent mille vaillants hommes pour cent talents d\u2019argent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.7","name":"2 Chroniques 25:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.5","name":"2 Chroniques 25:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Un homme de Dieu vint aupr\u00e8s de lui, et dit: O roi, qu\u2019une arm\u00e9e d\u2019Isra\u00ebl ne marche point avec toi, car l\u2019\u00c9ternel n\u2019est pas avec Isra\u00ebl, avec tous ces fils d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.8","name":"2 Chroniques 25:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.6","name":"2 Chroniques 25:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Si tu vas avec eux, quand m\u00eame tu ferais au combat des actes de vaillance, Dieu te fera tomber devant l\u2019ennemi, car Dieu a le pouvoir d\u2019aider et de faire tomber.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.9","name":"2 Chroniques 25:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.7","name":"2 Chroniques 25:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Amatsia dit \u00e0 l\u2019homme de Dieu: Et comment agir \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard des cent talents que j\u2019ai donn\u00e9s \u00e0 la troupe d\u2019Isra\u00ebl? L\u2019homme de Dieu r\u00e9pondit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel peut te donner bien plus que cela.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.10","name":"2 Chroniques 25:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.8","name":"2 Chroniques 25:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Alors Amatsia s\u00e9para la troupe qui lui \u00e9tait venue d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, afin que ces gens retournassent chez eux. Mais ils furent tr\u00e8s irrit\u00e9s contre Juda, et ils s\u2019en all\u00e8rent chez eux avec une ardente col\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.11","name":"2 Chroniques 25:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.9","name":"2 Chroniques 25:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Amatsia prit courage, et conduisit son peuple. Il alla dans la vall\u00e9e du sel, et il battit dix mille hommes des fils de S\u00e9ir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.12","name":"2 Chroniques 25:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.10","name":"2 Chroniques 25:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Et les fils de Juda en saisirent dix mille vivants, qu\u2019ils men\u00e8rent au sommet d\u2019un rocher, d\u2019o\u00f9 ils les pr\u00e9cipit\u00e8rent; et tous furent \u00e9cras\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.13","name":"2 Chroniques 25:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.11","name":"2 Chroniques 25:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Cependant, les gens de la troupe qu\u2019Amatsia avait renvoy\u00e9s pour qu\u2019ils n\u2019allassent pas \u00e0 la guerre avec lui firent une invasion dans les villes de Juda depuis Samarie jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Beth-Horon, y tu\u00e8rent trois mille personnes, et enlev\u00e8rent de nombreuses d\u00e9pouilles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.14","name":"2 Chroniques 25:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.12","name":"2 Chroniques 25:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.015,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Guerre funeste avec Joas, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Conspiration contre Amatsia; sa mort<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 14-28: cf. 2 Ch 28:23. 2 R 14:8-20. J\u00e9 2:19.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019Amatsia fut de retour apr\u00e8s la d\u00e9faite des \u00c9domites, il fit venir les dieux des fils de S\u00e9ir, et se les \u00e9tablit pour dieux; il se prosterna devant eux, et leur offrit des parfums.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.15","name":"2 Chroniques 25:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.13","name":"2 Chroniques 25:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Alors la col\u00e8re de l\u2019\u00c9ternel s\u2019enflamma contre Amatsia, et il envoya vers lui un proph\u00e8te, qui lui dit: Pourquoi as-tu recherch\u00e9 les dieux de ce peuple, quand ils n\u2019ont pu d\u00e9livrer leur peuple de ta main?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.16","name":"2 Chroniques 25:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.14","name":"2 Chroniques 25:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Comme il parlait, Amatsia lui dit: Est-ce que nous t\u2019avons fait conseiller du roi? Retire-toi! Pourquoi veux-tu qu\u2019on te frappe? Le proph\u00e8te se retira, en disant: Je sais que Dieu a r\u00e9solu de te d\u00e9truire, parce que tu as fait cela et que tu n\u2019as pas \u00e9cout\u00e9 mon conseil.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.17","name":"2 Chroniques 25:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.15","name":"2 Chroniques 25:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s s\u2019\u00eatre consult\u00e9, Amatsia, roi de Juda, envoya dire \u00e0 Joas, fils de Joachaz, fils de J\u00e9hu, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Viens, voyons-nous en face!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.18","name":"2 Chroniques 25:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.16","name":"2 Chroniques 25:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et Joas, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, fit dire \u00e0 Amatsia, roi de Juda: L\u2019\u00e9pine du Liban envoya dire au c\u00e8dre du Liban: Donne ta fille pour femme \u00e0 mon fils! Et les b\u00eates sauvages qui sont au Liban pass\u00e8rent et foul\u00e8rent l\u2019\u00e9pine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.19","name":"2 Chroniques 25:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.17","name":"2 Chroniques 25:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.19","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:19","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Tu as battu les \u00c9domites, penses-tu, et ton c\u0153ur s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve pour te glorifier. Reste maintenant chez toi. Pourquoi t\u2019engager dans une malheureuse entreprise, qui am\u00e8nerait ta ruine et celle de Juda?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.20","name":"2 Chroniques 25:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.18","name":"2 Chroniques 25:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.20","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:20","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Mais Amatsia ne l\u2019\u00e9couta pas, car Dieu avait r\u00e9solu de les livrer entre les mains de l\u2019ennemi, parce qu\u2019ils avaient recherch\u00e9 les dieux d\u2019\u00c9dom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.21","name":"2 Chroniques 25:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.19","name":"2 Chroniques 25:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.21","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:21","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et Joas, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, monta; et ils se virent en face, lui et Amatsia, roi de Juda, \u00e0 Beth-Sch\u00e9mesch, qui est \u00e0 Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.22","name":"2 Chroniques 25:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.20","name":"2 Chroniques 25:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.22","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:22","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Juda fut battu par Isra\u00ebl, et chacun s\u2019enfuit dans sa tente.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.23","name":"2 Chroniques 25:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.21","name":"2 Chroniques 25:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.23","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:23","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Joas, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, prit \u00e0 Beth-Sch\u00e9mesch Amatsia, roi de Juda, fils de Joas, fils de Joachaz. Il l\u2019emmena \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et il fit une br\u00e8che de quatre cents coud\u00e9es dans la muraille de J\u00e9rusalem, depuis la porte d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la porte de l\u2019angle.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.24","name":"2 Chroniques 25:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.22","name":"2 Chroniques 25:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.24","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:24","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Il prit tout l\u2019or et l\u2019argent et tous les vases qui se trouvaient dans la maison de Dieu, chez Obed-\u00c9dom, et les tr\u00e9sors de la maison du roi; il prit aussi des otages, et il retourna \u00e0 Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.23","name":"2 Chroniques 25:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.25","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:25","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Amatsia, fils de Joas, roi de Juda, v\u00e9cut quinze ans apr\u00e8s la mort de Joas, fils de Joachaz, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.26","name":"2 Chroniques 25:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.24","name":"2 Chroniques 25:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.26","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:26","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le reste des actions d\u2019Amatsia, les premi\u00e8res et les derni\u00e8res, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des rois de Juda et d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.27","name":"2 Chroniques 25:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.27","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:27","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Depuis qu\u2019Amatsia se fut d\u00e9tourn\u00e9 de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, il se forma contre lui une conspiration \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et il s\u2019enfuit \u00e0 Lakis; mais on le poursuivit \u00e0 Lakis, o\u00f9 on le fit mourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.28","name":"2 Chroniques 25:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.26","name":"2 Chroniques 25:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.28","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 25:28","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.025.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.026.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.25.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>On le transporta sur des chevaux, et on l\u2019enterra avec ses p\u00e8res dans la ville de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25","name":"2 Chroniques 25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.26.1","name":"2 Chroniques 26:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.26.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.27","name":"2 Chroniques 25:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb34bee23.16948466');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb34bee23.16948466\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb34bee23.16948466","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb34bee23.16948466'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb34bee23.16948466\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}